      <hedline>
        <hl1>NAPSTER.COM SEES VISITORS SURGE</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Graph depicts surge in traffic at Web site operated by Napster.com after company was ordered by federal judge to stop permitting its users to trade copyrighted music files</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>After Napster.com was ordered by a federal judge to stop permitting its users to trade copyrighted music files, traffic on the site surged. Averaging 220,000 visitors a day, Napster was the 19th most active site for the week ending July 30.</p>
      </block>
